{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"update"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this method to update the appearance of the user location annotation. This"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method is called by the associated map view when it has determined that the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"user location annotation needs to be updated. This can happen in response to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"user interaction, a change in the user’s location, when the user tracking mode"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"changes, or when the viewport changes."}]},{"type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"During user interaction with the map, this method may be called many"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"times to update the user location annotation. Therefore, your implementation of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this method should be as lightweight as possible to avoid negatively affecting"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"performance."}]}],"name":"Note"}]}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView\/update","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNUserLocationAnnotationView(im)update","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNUserLocationAnnotati